# Security Policy

## Supported Node.js version

| Version | Supported          |
| ------- | ------------------ |
| 19.x   | :white_check_mark: |
| 18.x   | :white_check_mark:                |
| 14.x   | :white_check_mark: |
| 12.x   | :white_check_mark:                |
| < 12.0   | :x:                |
